						</a>
					</li>
					<li>
						<a target="_blank" href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=http%3A//www.wowthemes.net">
							<svg class="svgIcon-use" width="29" height="29" viewbox="0 0 29 29">
